<h1>Recorded sessions</h1>
<p>The following figure shows us the table of recorded sessions of certain student. It displays all we have submitted into the database along with all information such as date, teacher, meeting duration and so on. </p>
<img width="100%" src="../others/howto/images/course.png">
<p>We can click on each column to sort the records based on things we need to, for example, we want to sort them based on meeting number, the date (such as the newest/oldest), based on certain tutors etc. </p>
<p>We can also do search using field right above the table to find specific information, for example certain topics (greeting, conditional sentence etc), or keywords like review and so on. </p>
